{"tid":2123921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果見到你嘅屋企人比人打到仆街你會點做？","createTime":"2020-07-25T04:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T08:52:14.000Z","uid":204401,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ced267f30c2619f88aab0f6d36d18628040d521d","tid":2123921,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">緊係即刻還拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我地依加YouTube戰線比人打到仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當手足係屋企人嘅你，仲唔即刻做任？<br />\n記得share埋你嘅親朋戚友一齊做任阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中文版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQ7sDTT9kPQ&amp;bpctr=1595595400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXQ7sDTT9kPQ%26bpctr%3D1595595400&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=17eeb51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQ7sDTT9kPQ&amp;bpctr=1595595400</a><br />\n<br />\n英文版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5w69QySL6zM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5w69QySL6zM&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=e8b2c4e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5w69QySL6zM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">整合版</span><br />\n黑警洗白片《暗夜星辰》重新再Upload, 鍵戰請用電腦版做任!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123425\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123425</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n用電腦版最直接簡單<br />\n電話轉做桌面網頁版顯示都有可能成功<br />\n<br />\n見到警告, 按 同意繼續觀看<br />\n<br />\n1) 入到去先停播 或 直接跳到第2步 <br />\n(停播有可能被YouTube認為spam)<br />\n<br />\n2) dislike + report <br />\n仇恨, 暴力, 恐怖主義, 不實<br />\n<br />\n3) 有時間可以LIKE埋 &quot;講真話&quot; 留言<br />\n<br />\n4) dislike report完 可以去觀看記錄個到del左個views佢<br />\n<br />\n5) 繼續 dislike + report 以下相關片段"},{"pid":"b936b6e7dc50fcb4c5b296